{"tid":796696,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"排隊買劉德華演唱會門票被斬案 警拉黑底「拓海」","createTime":"2018-08-28T02:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T05:06:05.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"199c79dfdcfa206b1b761c629663dd09aad699bd","tid":796696,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180828/large/1535421925_6468.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180828%2Flarge%2F1535421925_6468.jpg&h=89d240a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩日前於柴灣青年廣場城市售票網，排隊購買劉德華演唱會門票的58歲姓鄭內地男子，與兩名操本地話男子爭執，更被其中一人用利刀襲擊，左手及左耳中刀受傷。<br />\n<br />\n東區反黑組接手調查，至今日凌晨約1時，在柴灣耀興道一單位拘捕一名26歲姓譚涉案男子。涉嫌串謀有意圖傷人，現正被扣查。<br />\n<br />\n據知譚男為黑幫新義安小頭目，人稱「拓海」，有指他當晚曾到現場，向每名排隊人士提出：「我畀你排廿個位無問題，到時留幾個位畀我。」疑被斬內地男子拒絕惹禍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180828/58615105\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180828%2F58615105&d=Mtxf%2FLmfa2MhPr1aEs7ilwtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=ebf88196\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180828%2F58615105&h=8888023b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180828/58615105</a>"},{"pid":"e94cf84a2424bc2b5020496d457c8030c9aaa093","tid":796696,"uid":39698,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T02:59:13.000Z","msg":"三萬蚊過夜你條女係雞呀"},{"pid":"62e175249df02b2478922d7418cf2e38ddba4fd2","tid":796696,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T03:50:59.000Z","msg":"得閒嚟油麻地搵我"},{"pid":"fedd6eec812df484e061a2e3c224a247eb0a18a0","tid":796696,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T05:06:05.000Z","msg":"排隊購買劉德華演唱會門票的58歲姓鄭<span style=\"color